  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.5">
<l>pāyntāṉait tiricakaṭam pāṟi vīḻap pālakaṉā yālilaiyil paḷḷi yiṉpa</l>
<l>mēyntāṉai yilaṅkoḷicēr maṇikkuṉ ṟaṉṉa vīriraṇṭu mālvaraittō ḷemmāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>tōyntāṉai nilamakaḷtōḷ tūtiṟ ceṉṟap poyyaṟaivāyp pukappeyta mallar maṅkak</l>
<l>kāyntāṉai yemmāṉaik kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ kaṭipoḻilcūḻ kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who leaped on the rolling cart so it fell in pieces,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who as a baby was worthy of happiness</l>
<l rend="indent">on the bed on a banyan leaf,</l>
<l>Our lord with two-by-two dark, boulder[-like] arms,</l>
<l rend="indent">which resemble beautiful sapphire mountains of glittering light,</l>
<l>The one who caressed the shoulders of lady earth, the one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">arriving as an envoy, when he went into that false chamber,</l>
<l>Destroyed the wrestlers who were placed [there]</l>
<l rend="indent">when he overpowered [them], our lord</l>
<l>I saw for myself in Talacayaṉam encircled by fragrant gardens at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
